    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twas the night before Christmas</strong>, when the Anderson family discovered a holiday whodunit. Their holiday decorations had vanished without a trace, leaving only a mysterious strand of red yarn behind…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determined to save their Christmas spirit, the Andersons donned their detective hats and embarked on a festive investigation that would take them through every hidden nook and cranny of their charming house!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the magical glowing yarn through the enchanting match-3 puzzles, jigsaws, and other mini-games. Explore the family's home, from the basement to the snow-covered garden, uncovering clues and collecting lost ornaments along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you be able to save their Christmas and bring the family together?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging story-driven gameplay with a cosy Christmas theme</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 challenging match-3 levels with unique holiday-themed obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adorn the family house with the Christmas theme decorations!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun mini-games including jigsaws, memory games, and slider puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful, festive graphics and charming character animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Family-friendly content perfect for all ages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable gameplay options</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CE VERSION ADD-ONS:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 Match-3 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Jigsaws</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Slider Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 